{"tid":261351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【六四遊行】支聯會：1000人參與遊行　創9年新低　警方：最高峰450人","createTime":"2017-05-28T11:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T12:43:33.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfef1154a53ca01d1ee012e27d64771b872ff1a9","tid":261351,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170528/s00001/14071cbdfbd598e2339ee1b074258f12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170528%2Fs00001%2F14071cbdfbd598e2339ee1b074258f12.jpg&h=eee1698b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支聯會今午3時舉行六四遊行，由灣仔修頓球場出發，約黃昏6時抵達中聯辦後散去。大會公布今年遊行人數為1000人，創下9年新低，但副主席蔡耀昌稱對遊行人數感滿意，形容是「不太差」，因過往市民也是多集中參與六四晚會。他相信，遊行人數與六四晚會人數沒有直接關連，預料最少有10萬人出席六四晚會。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，今日六四遊行最高峰時有約450人。<br />\n<br />\n蔡耀昌形容，遊行出席人數多是值得振奮，人數少則是一種鞭策，讓支聯會繼續努力，強調無論人數多少，支聯會都會繼續舉辦遊行。<br />\n<br />\n遊行隊伍今日一度就開放西邊街行車路問題，與警方發生推撞，警方一度出示紅旗警告，並帶走支聯會常委梁錦威，其後遊行隊伍獲放行，梁錦威亦獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n蔡耀昌批評，警方安排失當引致衝突，指事前曾通知警方有意使用行車路，但承認警方早前批出的不反對通知書，只允許遊行隊伍使用行人路。<br />\n<br />\n梁錦威表示，警方帶他到西區警署後，記錄他的個人資料，稱會再作調查，但未有拘捕他，逗留一會後便獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170528/s00001/1495969794007?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170528%2Fs00001%2F1495969794007%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=Wx0eNyw6v6BFVWji7AgE%2Bf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=50349f2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170528%2Fs00001%2F1495969794007%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=93b97c31\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170528/s00001/1495969794007?web_push=1</a>"},{"pid":"8fdda60c07840ff1be4a87bfda5b2d7ff23b22a8","tid":261351,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:32:54.000Z","msg":"鄰國啲野關你撚事咩支那昌"},{"pid":"ca9e0cd3885cecdc0aa8cf6fd35f3deff2fe59cc","tid":261351,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"(1000 + 450) / 2 = 725"},{"pid":"e32ad0f4380e73712fde8f2c85430f55bcd13fa2","tid":261351,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"550a9c4befbdd9531f255b8dd626bc7ca2c30563","tid":261351,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:35:19.000Z","msg":"香港市民支援<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">愛國</span></span>民主運動聯合會<br />\n<br />\n你班友好愛支那國呀？"},{"pid":"5ae902962169a37ef60cb097ed0e85e0b4c9d626","tid":261351,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:35:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次我絕對支持警察拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&gt;&gt; 帶走支聯會常委梁錦威，其後遊行隊伍獲放行，梁錦威亦獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n夾埋做戲架咋"},{"pid":"36569a66185d1e4ff0a45c89eb4272a5751215d4","tid":261351,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:36:17.000Z","msg":"真係可悲，又少一個反抗聲音"},{"pid":"0c802ca3a00cae7212ddab0e5c8f2b8909597bba","tid":261351,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係可悲，又少一個反抗聲音</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a038420de057ccaa88f096b13c4a654a46142b39","tid":261351,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:37:02.000Z","msg":"鄰國既人都唔撚理,我點解要理<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ee5107571bb7f03aac4ea8d657d029493a8b04","tid":261351,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lom